    public class PageTools

    The PageTools class provides utility methods for interacting with web elements using Selenium WebDriver. It includes methods for clicking elements, typing text, retrieving text, and waiting for elements to be visible on the page.

    This class extends DefaultLogger for logging capabilities and uses DriverManager to obtain the WebDriver instance.

    The class is also annotated with LocatorAutoFixer to enable automatic locator correction in case of issues.
